snippet.textDisplay: For those confused, the National Pork Board is a USA commodity program funded by our Department of Agriculture (& pork producers themselves) & its sole purpose is to research, subsidize & market the pork industry. "Beef: It's What's for Dinner" & "The Incredible, Edible Egg."
